## 🎯 Key Features

✨ **Context Pruning:**
- 3-stage pipeline reduces 2000 → 400 tokens
- BM25 keyword filter (Stage 1)
- FAISS semantic reranker (Stage 2)
- Token budget enforcer (Stage 3)

✨ **Cost Optimization:**
- $0.77 → $0.15 per query (80% savings)
